@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "About Us";
}

<style>
    .about-container {
        max-width: 1000px;
        margin: 50px auto;
        padding: 30px;
        background: linear-gradient(to right, #e0f7fa, #ffffff);
        border-radius: 20px;
        box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
        transition: all 0.3s ease-in-out;
    }

        .about-container:hover {
            transform: scale(1.01);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 30px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
        }

    .about-title {
        font-size: 36px;
        font-weight: bold;
        color: #0d47a1;
        text-align: center;
        margin-bottom: 20px;
    }

    .about-text {
        font-size: 18px;
        line-height: 1.8;
        color: #333;
        text-align: justify;
        animation: fadeIn 1.2s ease-in-out;
    }

    .highlight {
        color: #004d40;
        font-weight: bold;
    }

    .college-image {
        width: 100%;
        border-radius: 15px;
        margin-bottom: 25px;
        box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.2);
        transition: transform 0.4s ease;
    }

        .college-image:hover {
            transform: scale(1.02);
        }

    @@keyframes fadeIn {
        from

    {
        opacity: 0;
        transform: translateY(20px);
    }

    to {
        opacity: 1;
        transform: translateY(0);
    }

    }
</style>

<div class="about-container">
    <div class="about-title">About Vishal College of Engineering, Solapur</div>

    <!-- Add College Image -->
    <img src="/images/college.jpg" alt="College Building" class="college-image" />


    <div class="about-text">
        <p>
            <span class="highlight">Vishal College of Engineering, Solapur</span> was founded in the year 2000 with a commitment to deliver high-quality engineering education and foster innovation.
        </p>
        <p>
            Over the years, the college has evolved into one of the most reputed institutions in the region, known for its academic excellence, vibrant campus life, and strong industry connections.
        </p>
        <p>
            The college offers undergraduate and postgraduate programs across disciplines such as <span class="highlight">Computer Engineering, Information Technology, Civil, Mechanical, and AI & Data Science</span>.
        </p>
        <p>
            With a team of experienced faculty and state-of-the-art infrastructure, the institution provides students with the right environment to grow intellectually and professionally.
        </p>
        <p>
            Our mission is to empower students with knowledge, creativity, and the confidence to face global challenges. We aim to produce not just engineers, but future leaders and innovators.
        </p>
    </div>
</div>
